Gem Diamonds Says Letseng Achieved $4,272 Per Carat For Its April Exports

-- B y   A m a n d a   J o r d a n
-- 
2011-04-20T06:11:08Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-20/gem-diamonds-says-letseng-achieved-4-272-per-carat-for-its-april-exports.html
Gem Diamonds Ltd. (GEMD) , a producer of
the stones in southern  Africa , said its Letseng project in
 Lesotho  achieved an average value of $4,272 a carat for its
April exports, bringing the average value to $3,067 a carat for
the period since Jan. 1. The company commented in a statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Amanda Jordan in London at 
 ajordan11@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
